section.p:
For example:

Timer t = new Timer();
for (int i = 0; i < 100; i++) {
  t.start();
  // ... the code being measured ...
  t.stop();
}

System.out.println("timer results, n=" + t.size());
System.out.println("  mean=" + t.mean() + " stdev=" + t.standardDeviation());
System.out.println("  min=" + t.min() + " max=" + t.max());
